                <a href="https://github.com/ucli-tools/ucli-registry" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition">GitHub</a> ‚Ä¢
                <a href="https://github.com/ucli-tools" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition ml-4">Organization</a>
            </p>
        </div>
